{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, your, your question was, what was my early concept of, of Nazis?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I, I, I, I-- even as a young man, I have been a very realistic person.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, I had arguments with my uncles, right, which was completely unconventional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they have been foolhardy-- because they have been unduly optimistic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had this easy attitude, well, everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I, I, I saw-- I knew that everything will not be all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that time, I was helpless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's nothing I could do-- absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is very difficult for you people to understand why, you know, so many people went to, to the abattoir, you know, without actually resisting and proving and trying to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we are still at the early stages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are going to come to the-- to the-- you know, when, when, when life was really in danger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this stage, you know, it was no life danger yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are in 1942, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And, and the, the, [LAUGHS] the propaganda coming from the radio-- we didn't have television-- from the papers, from the pulpit, from everywhere, was so misguided and it was so concentrated, right, that it was obviously-- what Hitler was, was determined to do is to, to, to reduce us to a-- to a, a status of the cockroach, of a-- of a vermin, right?",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to kill a cockroach, there is no problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You put your foot on that cockroach, and you don't have any bad conscience, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the atmosphere towards which the propaganda was building up to-- and very successfully, I must, must admit.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
